{"tid":178012,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2017DSE]四條prog+你問我答","createTime":"2017-03-29T08:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T13:20:06.000Z","uid":37614,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b55c8c044d11c322b9faeda6e341bc040fa91b","tid":178012,"uid":37614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:57:40.000Z","msg":"利申先 <br />\n本人都只係2017dser 只係我自己對大學冇望<br />\n希望幫下啲想入大學而差依科嘅人 大家2017加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02878ae850ac09e61f459764c7d4702ec15396fa","tid":178012,"uid":37614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:01:38.000Z","msg":"Prog1 completing square/配方法<br />\n改左少少公式 因為同formula01重覆<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/173932_121e8fff660e113f290af13dc6659bef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2F173932_121e8fff660e113f290af13dc6659bef.jpg&h=ce4cd661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用法：ax^2+bx+c=0<br />\n配方法：a(x-h)^2+k=0<br />\n首先call個programme出黎<br />\n順次序入abc 三個數<br />\n例如x^2+4x+1=0<br />\n入1  4  1<br />\n首先會出vertex/頂點x(即h) -2<br />\n頂點y(即k) -3<br />\n判別式 12<br />\n如果個x係無理數嘅會有以下數字出現<br />\n繼續用x^2+4x+1=0做例子<br />\n-2  1  3。  &lt;==x intercept 嘅答案<br />\n首先抄翻個a=1落去(因為<strong><ins>1</ins></strong>x^2+4x+1)<br />\n就會得出<br />\n1(x+2)^2-3=0<br />\n頂點（-2,-3）<br />\nx=-2<ins>+</ins>1&radic;3<br />\nBtw 各位巴絲有咩maths問題可以下面問"},{"pid":"e5ce4bff15aecdccbac9a0be9b79addb9a6e0ca0","tid":178012,"uid":37614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"第二條方程我會叫佢做聯立方程就算<br />\n事關佢又可以計圓形直線方程交點<br />\n又可以計兩條直線交點<br />\n一條式就ko晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/16/084643_b896af6d5a97e68f0c4707d8f6774b76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F084643_b896af6d5a97e68f0c4707d8f6774b76.jpg&h=56adf1c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用法亦都好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先入直線後入圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大楷嘅由A入到I 如果冇果個數嘅話就0<br />\nAx+By+C=0<br />\nDx^2+Exy+Fy^2+Gx+Hy+I=0<br />\n如果係兩條直線嘅話會出個兩個數<br />\nEg.x+y+3=0             4x+3y-7=0<br />\n入法就會係 1 1 3 0 0 0 4 3 -7<br />\n第一個就會係x坐標 第二個就y坐標<br />\n而圓形直線嘅話就會出到四個數<br />\n交點一嘅x坐標<br />\n交點一嘅y坐標<br />\n交點二嘅x坐標<br />\n交點二嘅y坐標<br />\n外面或者你自己都有入到二元一次聯立<br />\n而依條就可以直接取代左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多番個位出黎入其他公式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec7d7e4a7d893815032f4044996c379746b08f5","tid":178012,"uid":37614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:05:15.000Z","msg":"第三條會係cosine formula(唔肯定係咪咁叫<br />\nABC為邊嘅長度<br />\n而abc係邊嘅對應角<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4b1x664.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4b1x664.jpg&h=7b47cf1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用法<br />\n首先你要有ABC 或者ABc之類<br />\n姐係三條邊 或者兩邊一角<br />\n注意兩邊一個隻角係未知邊嘅對應角<br />\nProg03（即依條）<br />\n邊邊邊角<br />\n剩係入三個數<br />\n如果三條邊嘅就 A B C 0<br />\n就會得出a b c 面積<br />\n如果係兩邊一角就 0 A B c<br />\n就會得出 C a b 面積<br />\n即係三邊就順次序嘅對應角+面積<br />\n兩邊一角就會出左角對應嘅邊再順序出對應角+面積"},{"pid":"3cccd4a894cedb7642cb8a9aa11da7e6449bf8cd","tid":178012,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:05:33.000Z","msg":"仲有一個位入咩好，想mc可以快啲清到一題都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家有<br />\n一元二次<br />\n一元三次<br />\nvertex <br />\n四心<br />\n圓心半徑<br />\ndistance 比例搵 equation <br />\n2pt出m&amp;y-int搵equation"},{"pid":"f8b57e7f3d71737b444674bb299c9b20e6a1ff39","tid":178012,"uid":37614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:09:44.000Z","msg":"第四條就唔解釋太多<br />\n事關本身都未用得熟 <br />\n同埋圖裡面已經有用法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/29/170935_6b31fc8e03b41a48a81a654fdf694a50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F29%2F170935_6b31fc8e03b41a48a81a654fdf694a50.jpg&h=8241a3e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0b8776805bc995c3b242ba2b28c95fd28179644","tid":178012,"uid":37614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有一個位入咩好，想mc可以快啲清到一題都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家有<br />\n一元二次<br />\n一元三次<br />\nvertex <br />\n四心<br />\n圓心半徑<br />\ndistance 比例搵 equation <br />\n2pt出m&amp;y-int搵equation</blockquote><br />\n你所指嘅一元二次係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFormula01果個？ 定係頂點？"},{"pid":"e568c88b16d3a3bf2cf5089dd8a19a8e07605f50","tid":178012,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:21:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9916e4dd5fb9e046268986d7f05c55b734931dd2","tid":178012,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:22:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f46ad4839f7e20ebd4ef29c23d51b915cc1612ce","tid":178012,"uid":37614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你等炒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放心預左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd00b2e0286f3aeea999fa6665d1af1c596e5264","tid":178012,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4147fa0fd6766b73ae3772690ff9f5dc00d805e1","tid":178012,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT