g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783ff1ddff02102c8dc2fcaa1582a2728661c2e9","tid":178012,"uid":12490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">比較少會問一元三次方程</span><br />\n所以不太建議入<br />\n一元二次可以用圓形直線代替</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因式定理咪問囉<br />\n樓主未操過paper?"},{"pid":"ccc4b52f5b66b33f561095196525c224869e547c","tid":178012,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:19:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}